### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Create Appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "storeId": "store-uuid-here",
  "serviceId": "service-uuid-here",
  "appointmentDate": "2024-12-25T10:00:00.000Z",
  "notes": "Please arrive 10 minutes early"
}

### Get All Appointments (Current User)
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Appointment by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/appointment-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Appointments by Store
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/store/store-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Available Time Slots
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/available-slots/store-uuid-here/service-uuid-here?date=2024-12-25

### Update Appointment
PUT {{baseUrl}}/appointments/appointment-uuid-here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "appointmentDate": "2024-12-25T14:00:00.000Z",
  "notes": "Updated notes"
}

### Cancel Appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments/appointment-uuid-here/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete Appointment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/appointments/appointment-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin Test Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments/admin/test

